{"tid":550646,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 95 小畫家重出江湖！","createTime":"2018-02-05T02:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T03:29:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d110eb3dbdc60094949dacde4cbefd65ff6288","tid":550646,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"微軟於Windows 10秋季創作者更新把「小畫家」變成「小畫家3D」，而原來的程式則放在Windows巿集供人下載，曾引起一時哄動。現在大家又是否習慣「小畫家3D」的操作？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8b/Paint_3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8b%2FPaint_3D.jpg&h=492990cf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在過渡同時，又有沒有開始想念以前Windows 95的元祖「小畫家」？早前有開發者Isaiah Odhner以JavaScript重製Windows 95、98及XP年代的小畫家，並於開源平台GitHub發布，大家按下連結即可使用網頁版的小畫家，回憶以前的創作點滴。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/2/1517475897_qE-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F2%2F1517475897_qE-1280w.png&h=014559f4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nJS Paint: <a href=\"http://jspaint.ml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjspaint.ml&d=wki6ITxkegJeqrB7EpOSB04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=be215416\" target=\"_blank\">http://jspaint.ml</a><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/科技/網頁版windows-95小畫家js-paint-114207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%2F%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E7%89%88windows-95%E5%B0%8F%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6js-paint-114207&d=wki6ITxkegJeqrB7EpOSB04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c533cf5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/科技/網頁版windows-95小畫家js-paint-114207</a>"},{"pid":"31211b85abe936c2804e223f0087ab706ae6bd7e","tid":550646,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"灰色布景主題、底下的排色盤和左邊的工具標誌，這個小畫家的外觀與以前的一模一樣，勾起不少兒時回憶，試畫公仔，所有工具都用過了，還可以儲存下載照片，永久保存回憶。不只原來的功能和外觀復刻重製，這個JavaScript版本的小畫家(或稱JS Paint)還有許多新功能，例如編輯透明圖層的圖片、無限復原動作、支援手機瀏覽器和SVG檔案，甚至設計GIF圖也可以。"},{"pid":"7d8d343f3fa904d9a2aaea463d4f7f73f6d1590e","tid":550646,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"一早玩過個網頁版小畫家, Ctrl+PrtScn後paste唔撚到落去, 垃圾! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}